---
title: TROOP TRACK - DATA FLOW ARCHITECTURE (DFD)
---

%% Simple DFD-style view: external entities -> processes -> central data store
flowchart LR

%% =========================================================
%% Styling
%% =========================================================
classDef entity fill:#d7f7df,stroke:#22c55e,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#052e16;
classDef process fill:#cfe6ff,stroke:#3b82f6,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#0b1f33;
classDef store fill:#f6d78b,stroke:#c08b00,stroke-width:2px,color:#111827;
classDef ext fill:#ffe4e6,stroke:#fb7185,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#4c0519;
classDef note fill:#f3f4f6,stroke:#6b7280,stroke-dasharray: 4 3,color:#111827;

%% =========================================================
%% External Entities (Actors)
%% =========================================================
Soldier[Soldier]:::entity
Clerk[Clerk]:::entity
Adjutant[Adjutant]:::entity

UI[Next.js UI<br/>Dashboards + Forms]:::process

Soldier -->|HTTP/HTTPS| UI
Clerk -->|HTTP/HTTPS| UI
Adjutant -->|HTTP/HTTPS| UI

%% =========================================================
%% Processes (merge route groups to keep it readable)
%% =========================================================
P1[Auth<br/>Login + Signup]:::process
P2[Soldier & Profile Mgmt<br/>Profile read/update<br/>Soldiers list/approve/delete]:::process
P3[Fitness Plans & Assignments<br/>Create plans + assign plans<br/>Fetch exercises]:::process
P4[Fitness Tests & IPFT<br/>Create/justify tests<br/>IPFT date + results]:::process
P5[Reports & Analytics<br/>Reports + PDF<br/>Charts + trends<br/>High-risk list]:::process

UI -->|REST| P1
UI -->|REST| P2
UI -->|REST| P3
UI -->|REST| P4
UI -->|REST| P5

%% =========================================================
%% Data Store (collapsed)
%% =========================================================
DB[(SQLite / SQLiteCloud<br/>DATABASE_URL<br/><br/>Tables:<br/>User, LoginSession,<br/>FitnessPlan, AssignedPlan,<br/>FitnessTest, Report, IpftDate)]:::store

%% =========================================================
%% Data flows (read/write) between processes and the store
%% =========================================================

P1 <--> |read/write| DB
P2 <--> |read/write| DB
P3 <--> |read/write| DB
P4 <--> |read/write| DB
P5 <--> |read/write| DB

%% =========================================================
%% Notes
%% =========================================================
JWTNote["Notes:<br/>• Auth uses JWT (lib/jwt.ts) + bcrypt (lib/auth.ts)<br/>• DB access uses @sqlitecloud/drivers (lib/sqlitecloud-client.ts)"]:::note
JWTNote --- P1
